                <span class="text-purple-500 font-black">•</span>
                <span>Observers in study trials were unable to see the smooth curves in the crest-colored set even when told they were there.</span>
              </li>
            
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
                <span class="text-purple-500 font-black">•</span>
